  "title": "In Samambaia-DF 2 people spotted a UFO moving &#8220;up and sideways&#8221;[1992]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/07/06/in-samambaia-df-2-people-spotted-a-ufo-moving-up-and-sideways1992/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1py",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>NOV 7th, 1992</strong>. 20:47. Duration: 30 minutes. In Samambaia region, Distrito Federal, two people observed, with the naked eye and in a cloudy sky, an unidentified flying object, moving &#8220;up and sideways&#8221;. The UFO, according to the witnesses, was round with the appearance of &#8220;a ping-pong ball&#8221;, and had an incandescent glow. The unknown object was observed flying fast about 10 km away from the observers going in the direction of the city of Goiânia-GO.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.331. “Questionário sobre ocorrência de objeto voador não identificado na região de Samambaia, Distrito Federal</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
